## Summary
Fix high severity security issue in `lib/response.js`.

## Vulnerability
| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| **ID** | V-001 |
| **Severity** | HIGH |
| **Scanner** | multi_agent_ai |
| **Rule** | `V-001` |
| **File** | `lib/response.js:267` |
